import React from 'react';
import { useForm, ValidationError } from '@formspree/react';
import {
  Box,
  FormControl,
  FormLabel,
  Input,
  Textarea,
  Button,
  Heading,
  VStack,
  Alert,
  AlertIcon
} from '@chakra-ui/react';

function ChapterApplicationForm() {
  const [state, handleSubmit] = useForm("mblrrajq");

  if (state.succeeded) {
    return (
      <Alert status="success" variant="subtle" flexDirection="column" alignItems="center" justifyContent="center" textAlign="center" height="200px">
        <AlertIcon boxSize="40px" mr={0} />
        <Heading size="md" mb={4} color="gray.700">Thank you for your application!</Heading>
        <Box color="gray.700">We will get back to you soon.</Box>
      </Alert>
    );
  }

  return (
    <Box bg="black">
      <form onSubmit={handleSubmit}>
        <VStack spacing={4}>
          <FormControl id="name" isRequired>
            <FormLabel color="gray.700">Name</FormLabel>
            <Input type="text" name="name" />
            <ValidationError prefix="Name" field="name" errors={state.errors} />
          </FormControl>

          <FormControl id="email" isRequired>
            <FormLabel color="gray.700">Email</FormLabel>
            <Input type="email" name="email" />
            <ValidationError prefix="Email" field="email" errors={state.errors} />
          </FormControl>

          <FormControl id="organization" isRequired>
            <FormLabel color="gray.700">Organization</FormLabel>
            <Input type="text" name="organization" />
            <ValidationError prefix="Organization" field="organization" errors={state.errors} />
          </FormControl>

          <FormControl id="role" isRequired>
            <FormLabel color="gray.700">Your Role</FormLabel>
            <Input type="text" name="role" />
            <ValidationError prefix="Role" field="role" errors={state.errors} />
          </FormControl>

          <FormControl id="description" isRequired>
            <FormLabel color="gray.700">Description of Your Chapter</FormLabel>
            <Textarea name="description" />
            <ValidationError prefix="Description" field="description" errors={state.errors} />
          </FormControl>

          <FormControl id="goals" isRequired>
            <FormLabel color="gray.700">Goals and Objectives</FormLabel>
            <Textarea name="goals" />
            <ValidationError prefix="Goals" field="goals" errors={state.errors} />
          </FormControl>

          <FormControl id="support" isRequired>
            <FormLabel color="gray.700">How Can We Support You</FormLabel>
            <Textarea name="support" />
            <ValidationError prefix="Support" field="support" errors={state.errors} />
          </FormControl>

          <Button type="submit" colorScheme="blue" isLoading={state.submitting}>
            Submit
          </Button>
        </VStack>
      </form>
    </Box>
  );
}

export default ChapterApplicationForm;
